time: 30 seconds

short_desc: bits in user group

question: |
    (a) How many bits are there in the user permissions field of a file? \\
    \vspace*{0.25in} \\
    (b) What do these bits represent? \\
    \vspace*{0.25in}

answer: |
    (a) There are \textbf{3 bits}. \\
    (b) Starting from the most significant bit, they represent read(r),
    write(w) and execute(x).

